
= Google Books Browser =

- Purpose -
Provide a PHP API that can be used to add google books to bookshelf - given the books title and author.




- Install -
All of the files are meant to live in a directory call "GoogleBooks".
Create this directory somewhere in the php include path, and then add all the files.



- Dependancies -
Zend_Gdata Library (http://code.google.com/apis/gdata/docs/client-libraries.html)

